### 15.2 — Reinstatement

If your rights are terminated under Section 15.1, they may be reinstated if:

- You cure the non-compliance within thirty (30) days of becoming aware of the violation, or
- IdeaNax expressly and in writing grants You reinstatement of your rights.

Reinstatement under this Section does not prevent IdeaNax from seeking remedies for any previous violations.

### 15.3 — Survival of Obligations

Upon termination of Your rights under this License, the following provisions shall survive termination and remain in full force: Sections 2 (Definitions), 12 (Warranty Disclaimer), 13 (Limitation of Liability), 15.3 (Survival), and 16 (Governing Law).

