## How to Apply This License

To apply the IdeaNax Open License 1.0 to your own Work, attach the following notice to each source file, replacing the placeholder fields:

```
[File name or description]
Copyright (c) [YEAR] [YOUR NAME OR ORGANIZATION]

Licensed under the IdeaNax Open License 1.0 (INOL-1.0).
This file is based on or derived from work originally created by IdeaNax (https://ideanax.com).
You may not use this file except in compliance with the License.

A copy of the License is included in the LICENSE file or available at:
https://ideanax.com/licenses/INOL-1.0
```

Additionally, include a `LICENSE` file in the root of your repository containing the full text of this License, and a `NOTICE` or `CREDITS` file containing the required attribution statement.

