## Attribution Notice Templates

Use one of the following templates for attribution in your product. Select the template most appropriate for your use case:

---

### Template A — README / Documentation

```markdown
## Credits and Attribution

This project is based on or includes work originally created by **IdeaNax**
(https://ideanax.com), used under the IdeaNax Open License 1.0 (INOL-1.0).

We gratefully acknowledge IdeaNax's contribution to this project.
For full license terms, see the LICENSE file or visit:
https://ideanax.com/licenses/INOL-1.0
```

---

### Template B — Software About Dialog

```
This software is built upon or derived from work originally created by
IdeaNax (https://ideanax.com).
Licensed under the IdeaNax Open License 1.0 (INOL-1.0).
```

---

### Template C — Source File Header

```
/*
 * This file is part of [Your Product Name].
 * Portions of this file are derived from work originally created by
 * IdeaNax (https://ideanax.com), licensed under INOL-1.0.
 *
 * Modifications made by: [Your Name]
 * Date: [Date]
 * Description: [Brief description of changes]
 */
```

---

### Template D — Modified Work NOTICE File

```
NOTICE — IdeaNax Attribution

This product includes or is derived from software originally created by
IdeaNax (https://ideanax.com), licensed under the IdeaNax Open License
1.0 (INOL-1.0). A copy of the license is available in the LICENSE file
or at https://ideanax.com/licenses/INOL-1.0.

This product has been modified from the original IdeaNax Work.

Modified by: [Your Name / Organization]
Date of Modification: [Date]

Files Modified:
  - [file1.ext] — [brief description of change]
  - [file2.ext] — [brief description of change]

All original copyright notices and license terms from IdeaNax have been
preserved in this distribution.
```

---

### Template E — Website / App Footer

```html
<p>Built on open-source software by
  <a href="https://ideanax.com">IdeaNax</a>, 
  licensed under the 
  <a href="https://ideanax.com/licenses/INOL-1.0">IdeaNax Open License 1.0</a>.
